D.WIZARD.SUMMARIES.MBTI=function(type){var m=D.MBTI[type];if(!m)return"";var labels={INTJ:"Strategic and independent. You see patterns others miss and plan several steps ahead.",INTP:"Analytical and curious. You love understanding how things work at a fundamental level.",ENTJ:"Decisive and driven. You naturally organize people and resources toward goals.",ENTP:"Innovative and energetic. You love exploring new possibilities and challenging ideas.",INFJ:"Insightful and principled. You understand people deeply and care about meaning.",INFP:"Idealistic and empathetic. You are guided by strong inner values and compassion.",ENFJ:"Charismatic and caring. You inspire others and build genuine connections.",ENFP:"Enthusiastic and creative. You see potential everywhere and energize those around you.",ISTJ:"Reliable and thorough. You value tradition, duty, and getting things done right.",ISFJ:"Nurturing and dependable. You remember details about people and take care of them quietly.",ESTJ:"Organized and direct. You create order and follow through on commitments.",ESFJ:"Warm and conscientious. You create harmony and make people feel welcome.",ISTP:"Practical and adaptable. You solve problems hands-on and stay cool under pressure.",ISFP:"Gentle and artistic. You experience life through your senses and values.",ESTP:"Bold and pragmatic. You thrive on action and live in the moment.",ESFP:"Spontaneous and fun. You bring joy to others and embrace life fully."};return"<strong>"+m.label+"</strong><br>"+(labels[type]||"")+"<br><br><strong>How this affects relationships:</strong> Your personality type influences how you communicate, handle conflict, and connect emotionally. The engine uses this to predict communication patterns and compatibility dynamics.";};
